Dialogue: 8,0:00:02.76,0:00:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask for an answer right away, but \Nwould you consider writing the story for this?
Dialogue: 8,0:00:07.56,0:00:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... I can't do that unless Mashiro agrees to it.
Dialogue: 8,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. That's right.
Dialogue: 8,0:00:14.48,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A-As long as it doesn't interfere with {\i1}PCP{\i0}, I'm...
Dialogue: 8,0:00:19.60,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}do{\i0} want Shiratori to get serialized.
Dialogue: 8,0:00:22.52,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want Takagi to progress as an author.
Dialogue: 8,0:00:26.45,0:00:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 8,0:00:27.66,0:00:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! Just don't make it better than {\i1}PCP{\i0}!
Dialogue: 8,0:00:32.33,0:00:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we'll submit this one-shot with Takagi as the author.
Dialogue: 8,0:00:36.62,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Polish up your storyboard a bit, and make a manuscript from it.
Dialogue: 8,0:00:40.14,0:00:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 8,0:00:40.91,0:00:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I would like to be able to submit this for October's Treasure{\i0},
Dialogue: 8,0:00:45.06,0:00:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's only 20 days until the application deadline.
Dialogue: 8,0:00:47.76,0:00:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should shoot for November?
Dialogue: 8,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it! I can make a manuscript in 20 days!
Dialogue: 8,0:00:52.74,0:00:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get this storyboard ready to make into a manuscript right away!
Dialogue: 8,0:00:56.45,0:00:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 8,0:00:57.22,0:00:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 8,0:00:58.65,0:01:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, here at the beginning...
Dialogue: 8,0:01:00.30,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's standing still, watching people talk...
Dialogue: 8,0:01:01.56,0:01:04.95,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shuujin can handle two stories now.
Dialogue: 8,0:01:06.20,0:01:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if this makes it to serialization... {But if this is serialized...}
Dialogue: 8,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 8,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two back-to-back meetings really took their toll.
Dialogue: 8,0:02:50.56,0:02:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if {\i1}Rabuta & Peace{\i0} will make it?
Dialogue: 8,0:02:52.96,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the story author, so it had better!
Dialogue: 8,0:02:56.34,0:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it. We'd be in trouble if a \Nstory by Ashirogi Mutou didn't make it.
Dialogue: 8,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean a story by Takagi Akito, right?
Dialogue: 8,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 8,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to use my real \Nname. I'll have to use an alias...
Dialogue: 8,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll change my alias.
Dialogue: 8,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But all this is just to prepare us \Nfor the future of Ashirogi Mutou.
Dialogue: 8,0:03:14.16,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 8,0:03:14.92,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work hard on {\i1}PCP{\i0} and make sure our next work becomes an anime!
Dialogue: 8,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our next work, huh.
Dialogue: 8,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you love this painting that much?
Dialogue: 8,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 8,0:03:36.34,0:03:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you could walk, you'd come in here and stare at that painting for hours.
Dialogue: 8,0:03:42.56,0:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom is arranging your study-abroad in Paris.
Dialogue: 8,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad about that?
Dialogue: 8,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is being a manga artist really that awful?
Dialogue: 8,0:03:53.69,0:03:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We have our appearances to keep up... and you wanted to be an artist, right?
Dialogue: 8,0:03:58.73,0:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can come look at this painting,
Dialogue: 8,0:04:02.26,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but Grandpa paid a lot of money to have it all to himself.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:07.03,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people can read manga with just a little money.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people can enjoy it.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,650)}Being a manga artist is a wonderful job.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, it's well drawn.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,45 pages in 20 days!
Dialogue: 8,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well!
Dialogue: 8,0:04:28.15,0:04:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honestly surprised you've gotten it this far.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This will definitely pass!
Dialogue: 8,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:33.56,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I became an assistant and got experience in inking.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go ahead and submit this to Treasure{\i0}, then.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:40.29,0:04:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you became an assistant, you had no intention of becoming a manga artist.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You were satisfied with just being able to draw.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I take it that you've changed your mind now, right?
Dialogue: 8,0:04:51.73,0:04:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 8,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 8,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you change his name,
Dialogue: 8,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't submit a manuscript to Treasure when a serialized author like Takagi is doing the story!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}Don't you remember what happened last time?!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I... completely forgot.
Dialogue: 8,0:05:06.94,0:05:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only doing the story this time, so I didn't think about it.
Dialogue: 8,0:05:10.62,0:05:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If Takagi's the author, you should have shown it to me as soon as you had a storyboard.
Dialogue: 8,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hand it over.
Dialogue: 8,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 8,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The art's good, too!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:23.83,0:05:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, we could aim for {\i1}NEXT{\i0}, or even {\i1}Jack{\i0}!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:27.37,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 8,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, we have to!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's aim for {\i1}Jack{\i0} itself!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:34.72,0:05:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.... okay.... okay!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:39.73,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi, he said that {\i1}Rabuta & Peace{\i0} will be \Npublished in the November 24th issue of {\i1}Jack{\i0}!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:45.99,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It will?!
Dialogue: 8,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought he submitted it to Treasure{\i0}...
Dialogue: 8,0:05:50.20,0:05:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With Takagi as the author, apparently Treasure was off limits...
Dialogue: 8,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 8,0:05:55.54,0:06:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, congrats! It was a good idea to make Takagi your author!
Dialogue: 8,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too!
Dialogue: 8,0:06:02.21,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it does well, Hattori will definitely push it towards serialization...
Dialogue: 8,0:06:06.51,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The timing was perfect. They just happened to have an opening for a one-shot...
Dialogue: 8,0:06:13.11,0:06:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's good that Shuujin is growing as an author.
Dialogue: 8,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that's true.
Dialogue: 8,0:06:20.54,0:06:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 8,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, Peace.
Dialogue: 8,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace, listen to this!
Dialogue: 8,0:06:26.62,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The manga I drew based on you and me is gonna be in {\i1}Jack{\i0}!
Dialogue: 8,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm home.
Dialogue: 8,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, what is "{\i1}Jack{\i0}"?
Dialogue: 8,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a manga magazine...
Dialogue: 8,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop working as a manga assistant.
Dialogue: 8,0:06:43.10,0:06:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 8,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do as you please anymore.
Dialogue: 8,0:06:46.62,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 8,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in 2nd this week, too.
Dialogue: 8,0:06:54.14,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Ashirogi's tenacity is pushing you in a good direction.
Dialogue: 8,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I can't afford to lose!
Dialogue: 8,0:06:58.97,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0} hasn't become an anime yet, after all.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:01.81,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}PCP{\i0} probably won't ever become an anime.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 8,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 8,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, because it's a perfect crime manga.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:11.98,0:07:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a limit to what you can do with "unorthodox"...
Dialogue: 8,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,TV stations have no backbone.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:16.94,0:07:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:18.01,0:07:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of rankings, they can't \Nhope to get much better than this.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If things go on like this, they won't surpass {\i1}CROW{\i0}.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:24.52,0:07:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is weird.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:26.64,0:07:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is?
Dialogue: 8,0:07:28.04,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This "{\i1}Rabuta & Peace{\i0}" in next week's issue.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi's writing the story?
Dialogue: 8,0:07:33.34,0:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He tried to rearrange his name, but you figured it out anyways?
Dialogue: 8,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it out from the story.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:39.51,0:07:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This part about people's real feelings—
Dialogue: 8,0:07:41.24,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi has a habit of writing about "people's true worth".
Dialogue: 8,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:45.24,0:07:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that {\i1}PCP{\i0} won't get an anime and won't surpass {\i1}CROW{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 8,0:07:48.91,0:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 8,0:07:49.94,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why is Takagi writing something like this?!
Dialogue: 8,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really...
Dialogue: 8,0:07:55.17,0:07:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, why is that a bad thing?
Dialogue: 8,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obviously wrong!
Dialogue: 8,0:07:58.11,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't write this! It's wrong! Wrong!
Dialogue: 8,0:08:11.36,0:08:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi speaking.
Dialogue: 8,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}PCP{\i0} is in 4th place?
Dialogue: 8,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rabuta{\i0}'s in 5th?!
Dialogue: 8,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's good enough to aim for a serialization.
Dialogue: 8,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, the manuscript is good.
Dialogue: 8,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, about {\i1}Rabuta & Peace{\i0}...
Dialogue: 8,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already writing {\i1}PCP{\i0}.
Dialogue: 8,0:08:34.86,0:08:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So whether or not I'm going to write the story for another serialization
Dialogue: 8,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is something I'd like take some time to think about.
Dialogue: 8,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 8,0:08:42.01,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you want to prioritize{\i1} PCP.
Dialogue: 8,0:08:44.25,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuujin, if you're worried about me, don't be. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 8,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Saikou...
Dialogue: 8,0:08:50.91,0:08:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honestly happy that you're improving yourself.
Dialogue: 8,0:08:54.74,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And Shiratori, you've tried so hard in such a short time.
Dialogue: 8,0:08:58.25,0:09:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get serialized after coming this far, right?
Dialogue: 8,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I do, but...
Dialogue: 8,0:09:03.51,0:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's too much of an inconvenience for Takagi...
Dialogue: 8,0:09:08.46,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, my parents are against it...
Dialogue: 8,0:09:12.75,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that if I want to draw, I should study abroad.
Dialogue: 8,0:09:17.46,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you want to draw manga or study abroad?
Dialogue: 8,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to draw manga.
Dialogue: 8,0:09:27.54,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then draw!
Dialogue: 8,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Takagi you want him to do the story!
Dialogue: 8,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you hesitating?
Dialogue: 8,0:09:35.23,0:09:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiratori, you may not know, but Takagi does.
Dialogue: 8,0:09:40.64,0:09:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows just how hard it is to get serialized.
Dialogue: 8,0:09:44.10,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And how many people want it, fight for it, \Nbut just break down and give up in the end.
Dialogue: 8,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't refuse an opportunity like this!
Dialogue: 8,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same as Mashiro.
Dialogue: 8,0:09:55.99,0:10:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, both you and Takagi have talent.
Dialogue: 8,0:10:00.23,0:10:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't become serialized on talent alone.
Dialogue: 8,0:10:04.23,0:10:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Getting a {\i1}Jack{\i0} serialization isn't easy.
Dialogue: 8,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 8,0:10:14.55,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it affects {\i1}PCP{\i0}, I'll pull out. {that's what he said}
Dialogue: 8,0:10:18.52,0:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to understand that.
Dialogue: 8,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 8,0:10:21.96,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 8,0:10:26.99,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for me to write for {\i1}Rabuta{\i0}?
Dialogue: 8,0:10:30.84,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop asking. Just do it.
Dialogue: 8,0:10:33.03,0:10:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also going to challenge myself.
Dialogue: 8,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm able to draw a bit faster...
Dialogue: 8,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to draw another manga by myself!
Dialogue: 8,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Since you can't get an anime with me as your partner,
Dialogue: 8,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to do it yourself?
Dialogue: 8,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 8,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 8,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to challenge myself.
Dialogue: 8,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To improve Ashirogi Mutou.
Dialogue: 8,0:11:14.18,0:11:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It may take some time to be able to draw two manga at once,
Dialogue: 8,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I put all my effort into it, I know I can do it.
Dialogue: 8,0:11:21.26,0:11:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,920)}If I can't, then it'd be pointless to even think about surpassing Eiji!
Dialogue: 8,0:11:27.40,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A rough sketch of one page alone \Ntakes me 93 minutes and 43 seconds.
Dialogue: 8,0:11:30.87,0:11:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this pace, 19 pages will take me about 30 hours.
Dialogue: 8,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without sacrificing quality...
Dialogue: 8,0:11:36.25,0:11:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I have to be faster and {\i0}improve{\i1} the quality!
Dialogue: 8,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to keep that in mind as I draw!
Dialogue: 8,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, I can finalize your plans for studying abroad in Paris, correct?
Dialogue: 8,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't study abroad.
Dialogue: 8,0:11:57.12,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you'll work at Dad's company?
Dialogue: 8,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do that either.
Dialogue: 8,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will you continue to be so unreasonable?
Dialogue: 8,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide on one or the other, quickly.
Dialogue: 8,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a manga artist.
Dialogue: 8,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 8,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That profession is shameful.
Dialogue: 8,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to draw manga!
Dialogue: 8,0:12:13.01,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't allow it, I'll run away from home!
Dialogue: 8,0:12:15.46,0:12:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,An innocent kid like you wouldn't be \Nable to make it out there alone.
Dialogue: 8,0:12:20.46,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for dinner.
Dialogue: 8,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you draw this, Shun?
Dialogue: 8,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really good at drawing.
Dialogue: 8,0:12:35.54,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show this to your dad.
Dialogue: 8,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace?
Dialogue: 8,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Peace.
Dialogue: 8,0:13:00.26,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll take Saikou a while before he's ready to draw two manga at once.
Dialogue: 8,0:13:05.31,0:13:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, until he can, I'll take on writing one more manga...
Dialogue: 8,0:13:09.46,0:13:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or is it impossible?
Dialogue: 8,0:13:11.05,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't even know if I can handle two yet...
Dialogue: 8,0:13:13.10,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, something's up with Shiratori.
Dialogue: 8,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Like what?
Dialogue: 8,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His hair's kinda oily. {thick}
Dialogue: 8,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And he always smells good, but today he doesn't.
Dialogue: 8,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep a close eye on him, don't you?
Dialogue: 8,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's sick and didn't take a bath last night?
Dialogue: 8,0:13:27.74,0:13:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't seem like a one-day thing!
Dialogue: 8,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely weird!
Dialogue: 8,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's wearing the same clothes as yesterday.
Dialogue: 8,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're dirty!
Dialogue: 8,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's weird, too!
Dialogue: 8,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 8,0:13:41.00,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiratori, sorry, but can you stay a bit after work?
Dialogue: 8,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 8,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You ran away from home?!
Dialogue: 8,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Peace right now?
Dialogue: 8,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's waiting outside.
Dialogue: 8,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can either work at your dad's company, or study abroad.
Dialogue: 8,0:13:59.83,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiratori, you want to be a manga artist, right?
Dialogue: 8,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 8,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I ran away from home.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:07.14,0:14:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I thought I'd be happy as long as I could draw.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:12.19,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I drew a storyboard that made it into {\i1}Jack{\i0}, I was so happy.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think about the millions of people that will be reading my work, I feel like it's all worth it.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:22.34,0:14:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that feeling, but you have to contact your family.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:26.91,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. They know I'm working at \Nyour studio, and they have the address.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't be sleeping outdoors.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. If they find out about it, they'll be even more worried.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:37.88,0:14:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay at my parents' house tonight.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't inconvenience them like—
Dialogue: 8,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:45.24,0:14:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's a realtor, so he'll find you a place.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:48.10,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 8,0:14:49.77,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 8,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, have you seen this?
Dialogue: 8,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The issue with Shun's manga in it?
Dialogue: 8,0:14:56.93,0:14:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been reading it lately, so I missed it.
Dialogue: 8,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately?
Dialogue: 8,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I read it when I'm out sometimes.
Dialogue: 8,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Shun and Peace, right?
Dialogue: 8,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 8,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun sure is something.
Dialogue: 8,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Things seem to have settled down. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 8,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 8,0:15:19.39,0:15:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably draw some students in the background on this page, don't you think?
Dialogue: 8,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 8,0:15:26.24,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I do a detailed sketch and then show it to you?
Dialogue: 8,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You should always show him the sketch!
Dialogue: 8,0:15:32.35,0:15:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 8,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Detailed?
Dialogue: 8,0:15:35.15,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,On my own manuscript, I would ink in a rough sketch directly.
Dialogue: 8,0:15:40.04,0:15:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiratori, could you draw Makoto \Nusing your method? On this page?
Dialogue: 8,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 8,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast!
Dialogue: 8,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is all?
Dialogue: 8,0:16:01.06,0:16:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, that's enough. We're going home.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I found my own apartment.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:08.06,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but why are you so against him drawing manga?
Dialogue: 8,0:16:13.13,0:16:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an inappropriate vocation for the son of the Shiratori family.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:16.42,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about appearances in the end.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to draw, go to an art school.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get into art school, study abroad.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:23.04,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All according to the plan you've laid out for me that will keep up appearances.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more to art than painting.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:29.04,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm suited for manga.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:31.34,0:16:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that now.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:32.91,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting my work recognized made me happy.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawing manga is fun!
Dialogue: 8,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense. It's just people playing at being artists.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not playing at anything!
Dialogue: 8,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're staking our life on it!
Dialogue: 8,0:16:45.02,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude. Please refrain from butting in on our family affairs.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying manga is "inappropriate" and that we're "playing around"...
Dialogue: 8,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really done it now.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it!
Dialogue: 8,0:16:55.25,0:16:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiratori and I will work together to make something great.
Dialogue: 8,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something the Shiratori family can be proud of!
Dialogue: 8,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiratori can do it.
Dialogue: 8,0:17:03.90,0:17:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to art, even I can learn from him!
Dialogue: 8,0:17:07.33,0:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He can become a manga artist that you're not embarrassed to talk about to anyone!
Dialogue: 8,0:17:13.09,0:17:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that becoming an unpopular painter would be better than him becoming a popular manga artist.
Dialogue: 8,0:17:17.79,0:17:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We could talk all day and never convince her.
Dialogue: 8,0:17:21.91,0:17:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga isn't as worthless as you think it is.
Dialogue: 8,0:17:26.31,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga is a form of fine art!
Dialogue: 8,0:17:29.38,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different from paintings—it's a form of expression that moves you and speaks directly to young people's hearts!
Dialogue: 8,0:17:35.76,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I consider it a form of fine art when I draw it!
Dialogue: 8,0:17:39.37,0:17:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga as fine art? Impossible.
Dialogue: 8,0:17:42.28,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Far from it. It's just entertainment for the masses.
Dialogue: 8,0:17:46.32,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't put it down so harshly!
Dialogue: 8,0:17:48.04,0:17:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}has{\i0} to be art!
Dialogue: 8,0:17:51.55,0:17:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, stop being unreasonable. If you want to draw, study abroad in Paris.
Dialogue: 8,0:17:56.62,0:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 8,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think manga is fine.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Hitomi?
Dialogue: 8,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been hiding it from you, but I read {\i1}Jack{\i0} often.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 8,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you read Shun's manga?
Dialogue: 8,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I?
Dialogue: 8,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:13.55,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad said it was great, too.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:16.16,0:18:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun is doing is best to stand up against you.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never done that before.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:24.28,0:18:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted it badly enough to run away.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Shun?
Dialogue: 8,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do it!
Dialogue: 8,0:18:29.01,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 8,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're serious, right?
Dialogue: 8,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's why I ran away from home.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:33.05,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't let me, I'll have to cut ties with my family.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun!
Dialogue: 8,0:18:37.48,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have to do that. Mom will understand.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:40.64,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she does insist on cutting ties with you for drawing manga...
Dialogue: 8,0:18:45.81,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and you give up, that's game over.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You go, girl!
Dialogue: 8,0:18:55.05,0:18:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you like! Dear, Hitomi, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 8,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, take care of Shun.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:03.87,0:19:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, don't just pop in for O-bon and New Year's.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come home whenever you can.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hitomi is a wonderful girl.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 8,0:19:17.66,0:19:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right now.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:19.77,0:19:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:20.48,0:19:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best to draw a great manga.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:22.19,0:19:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I give up, it's game over.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:24.68,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Man! I want someone to say that to me!
Dialogue: 8,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ugh.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not getting the balance between the hair and the face.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:38.93,0:19:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiratori can start inking just from this...
Dialogue: 8,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can do it like that...
Dialogue: 8,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How much can I simplify my rough sketches?
Dialogue: 8,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rest is just practice.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a serialization meeting yesterday.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:54.71,0:19:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otter no. 11{\i0} is on an eternal break.
Dialogue: 8,0:19:57.37,0:19:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A break!
Dialogue: 8,0:19:58.21,0:20:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, after four years as a manga artist, I've got a break!
Dialogue: 8,0:20:02.69,0:20:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternal?
Dialogue: 8,0:20:03.65,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 8,0:20:04.55,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The anime's over, and the volumes aren't selling.
Dialogue: 8,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the right time. You've got six weeks left.
Dialogue: 8,0:20:11.67,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore!
Dialogue: 8,0:20:12.52,0:20:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year, starting in April, they'll be publishing\N one-shots from popular authors over seven weeks
Dialogue: 8,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,, in an event called the Super Leaders Fest.
Dialogue: 8,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're practically guaranteed entry.
Dialogue: 8,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 8,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If my serialization's over, I'm taking a two-year vacation!
Dialogue: 8,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already made up my mind!
Dialogue: 8,0:20:26.61,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I tell you that Aoki is entering?
Dialogue: 8,0:20:29.59,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki is?
Dialogue: 8,0:20:30.91,0:20:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time of Blue Leaves{\i0} is in a rut, and doing pretty poorly. It's getting canned.
Dialogue: 8,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can {enter while}use{using} the excuse of aiming for a new serialization together to...
Dialogue: 8,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 8,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-It's Hiramaru.
Dialogue: 8,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both pretty unlucky, it seems.
Dialogue: 8,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}R-Right. But don't let it get you down.
Dialogue: 8,0:20:50.75,0:20:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I also entered the Leaders Fest, so let's both do our best.
Dialogue: 8,0:20:54.35,0:20:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiramaru... you're too kind, even though your serialization just ended, too.
Dialogue: 8,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um, er, thanks!
Dialogue: 8,0:21:02.10,0:21:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yoshida! Aoki said she wanted to go out to tea with me!
Dialogue: 8,0:21:05.54,0:21:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 8,0:21:06.30,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, of course! I told you, right?
Dialogue: 8,0:21:08.68,0:21:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! "Depressed girls are fragile!"
Dialogue: 8,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's easier to put the moves on them!"
Dialogue: 8,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your advice was spot-on!
Dialogue: 8,0:21:14.83,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Hiramaru!
Dialogue: 8,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need now are your final six chapters and a storyboard for your one-shot!
Dialogue: 8,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Instructor Yoshida!
Dialogue: 8,0:21:19.73,0:21:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One-shots are a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 8,0:21:22.22,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Leaders Fest?
Dialogue: 8,0:21:24.01,0:21:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Among the entries are Hiramaru and Aoki, whose series were recently canceled.
Dialogue: 8,0:21:29.71,0:21:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And the veterans Arai and Niizuma are also participating.
Dialogue: 8,0:21:33.20,0:21:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Niizuma's got two series going already.
Dialogue: 8,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Niizuma can probably pull it off.
Dialogue: 8,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like he wants to do it.
Dialogue: 8,0:21:40.94,0:21:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us enter it, too!
Dialogue: 8,0:21:44.66,0:21:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, on top of {\i1}PCP{\i0}, Takagi's got {\i1}Rabuta & Peace{\i0} going into the serialization committee.
Dialogue: 8,0:21:51.35,0:21:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be too much?
Dialogue: 8,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's too much of a burden on him, I'll do it alone!
Dialogue: 8,0:21:58.12,0:21:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 8,0:21:59.81,0:22:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have to!
Dialogue: 8,0:22:01.49,0:22:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have to?
Dialogue: 8,0:22:02.54,0:22:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori, if I wasn't working on {\i1}Rabuta & Peace{\i0}, you wouldn't have objected, right?
Dialogue: 8,0:22:09.22,0:22:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be unfair to Mashiro if we couldn't participate because of me.
Dialogue: 8,0:22:13.59,0:22:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're Ashirogi Mutou to the end!
Dialogue: 8,0:22:20.41,0:22:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 8,0:22:21.72,0:22:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 8,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then! We'll enter the Super Leaders Fest!
Dialogue: 8,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 8,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 8,0:24:15.74,0:24:18.58,Default,,0,0,20,,The Leaders Fest is turning out to be interesting.
Dialogue: 8,0:24:18.58,0:24:21.77,Default,,0,0,20,,It's wonderful to see authors \Ncompeting and raising each other up.
Dialogue: 8,0:24:21.77,0:24:23.93,Default,,0,0,20,,I wish someone would give {\i1}me{\i0} a raise!
Dialogue: 8,0:24:23.93,0:24:25.94,Default,,0,0,20,,Next time: Punch and Independence.
Dialogue: 8,0:24:25.94,0:24:28.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Becoming the leader is a crucial dream!
