Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:43.37,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}Hey, if I could go to where you are right now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:52.71,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}then I could accept losing my voice
