Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:58.35,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}The times when I fight and struggle and dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:02.90,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}of all the things I want in life is the best
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:07.53,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}That's when I feel the bond between us and our strength to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:12.12,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}Our view of the world overlaps and stimulates us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:16.70,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}Let us polish ourselves, be more like how we should be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:21.79,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}The future can be found on the path we walk
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:26.84,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}My comrades believe in different things than me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.60,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}Our pride clashes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:42.90,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}I can't give up on it, I have to do what my heart commands me to do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:45.19,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}I'm ready
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:49.65,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}I've got the unbending pride
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:52.82,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}to run to the top now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:24:01.21,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}This is my only choice, this is what I love and this is what I'll do
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:06.21,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}I don't know what tomorrow will be like
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:09.17,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}But I know that tomorrow, again,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.17,0:24:11.84,ed trans,,0,0,0,,{\be.5}we will do our best to get by
